      "message": "[🟡 Suggestion] Line 106: The macOS branch replaces LOCAL_HOSTVARS with only MACOSX_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET, so any host variables normally needed for cross/build tool selection are not propagated to libvpx configure. This can make macOS cross builds pick the wrong compiler/toolchain even though Android explicitly preserves HOSTVARS. Keep HOSTVARS and append the deployment target.\n```suggestion\nLOCAL_HOSTVARS\u003d$(HOSTVARS) MACOSX_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET\u003d$(MIN_OSX_VERSION)\n```",
